# Production DATABASE_URL di-set di Vercel Project Settings → Environment Variables
# (Neon PostgreSQL connection string, e.g. postgresql://user:pass@ep-xxx.neon.tech/db?sslmode=require)
# JANGAN set DATABASE_URL di file ini — akan di-override Vercel dashboard env, dan
# bisa break `prisma migrate deploy` di build (kalau pakai SQLite file: → P1002 timeout).
#
# Untuk local dev, gunakan .env.local (gitignored) dengan:
#   DATABASE_URL=file:/home/z/my-project/db/custom.db
#   ADMIN_SECRET=Shogun2000$
